    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="[April 2021, Bangladesh, cox's Bazar]Both refugee and host: Asset ownership: Asset ownership data was collected under three broad categories for REVA-4: productive agricultural assets, productive non-agricultural assets and non-productive/household assets (see details in Annex). Asset ownership for Rohingya and host community households has remained unchanged since 2019, with no notable cases of depletion or accumulation (Figure 30). Patterns in productive asset ownership among the host community reflect an agriculture-dependent economy in Ukhiya –Teknaf. However, the low ownership of advanced agricultural assets such as irrigation pumps and fishing boats is a cause for concern. 37"/>
